descriptionHtml:

[center][color=#00ffff][size=5][b][u]F.A.Q.[/u][/b][/size][/color][/center]

[center][color=#ff0000][size=3][i][b]What mods did you use?[/b][/i][/size][/color][/center]
[center][size=3]Look below, you nerd
[/size][/center]
[size=3]
[/size][center][size=3][b][i][color=#ff0000]ENB?[/color][/i][/b]
[/size][/center][size=3]
[/size][center][size=3]Rudy ENB Vanilla with Snapdragon DOF
[/size][/center][size=3]

[/size][center][color=#ff0000][size=3][b][i]Whats with the sword orientation?[/i][/b][/size][/color][/center][size=3]
[/size][center][size=3]I edited the sword position through RaceMenu to resemble the Witcher style orientation. I made a version without the positioning, don't worry.[/size][/center][size=3]

[/size][center][color=#ff0000][size=3]How do we get the kids to Pokemon Go to the polls?[/size][/color][/center][size=3]
[/size][center][size=3]Put a Snorlax in the booths and you'll get this:[/size][/center]
[center][youtube]MoYjVTbLWyo[/youtube][/center]

[center][color=#ff0000][size=3]Did you base this preset after someone real?
[/size][/color][/center][size=3]
[/size][center][size=3]Jacob Sartorius[/size][/center][size=3]

[/size][center][color=#ff0000][size=3]Why is this FAQ filled with horrible/stale memes?[/size][/color][/center][size=3]
[/size][center][size=3]Because I have crippling depression[/size][/center][size=3]

[/size][center][color=#ff0000][size=3]How did you put text in the main image?[/size][/color][/center][size=3]
[/size][center][size=3]MS Paint. And Imgur. Mainly Imgur.[/size][/center][size=3]

[/size][center][color=#ff0000][size=3]You never listed where the face tattoo is from[/size][/color][/center][size=3]
[/size][center][size=3]I forgot which mod. I fucked up my MO list and I'm scared of messing it up for the 11th time. It is most likely Rutah Tattoos.[/size][/center][size=3]

[/size][center][color=#ff0000][size=3]Will there be a new version of this[/size][/color][/center][size=3]
[/size][center][size=3]This is a RaceMenu preset that took me 5 minutes to make and your asking me if I'm going to update...

[/size][center][size=3][color=#ff0000]Is that an OSA profile I see? ( ͡° ͜ʖ ͡°)[/color] [/size][/center][size=3]
[/size][center][size=3]Its cringy as fuck, but hey why the fuck not?

[color=#ff0000]OMG this looks so generic!

[youtube]piGKh_PVRoc[/youtube]

[/color][/size][/center][color=#ff0000][size=3]Gimmie some weeb shit

[youtube]YvLsWydCkzQ[/youtube][youtube]WbKxC8ssIdQ[/youtube][/size][/color]
